<title>
No Gear Shift to 4th Gear
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70B5104018001">
<title>
Symptom Description
</title>
<ptxt>
TCM does not shift gear to 4th gear under any of the following conditions.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
O/D off switch is turned ON.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Engine coolant temperature is less than 50 &#176;C (122 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ATF temperature is less than 20 &#176;C (68 &#176;F).
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ATF temperature is more than 150 &#176;C (302 &#176;F) and TCM is detecting P2762, P2763 and P2764.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM detects the following DTCs.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
P0712 / P0713 / P0717 / P0722 / P0787 / P0788 / P0961 / P0962 / P0963 / P0973 / P0974 / P0976 / P0977 / P1702 / U0073 / U0100
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfosub>
